in the car anyway.

29
00:01:24,100 --> 00:01:25,200
A surprise.

30
00:01:25,200 --> 00:01:26,800
Ugh, no more surprises,
please.

31
00:01:26,800 --> 00:01:28,100
No, this is
a good one,

32
00:01:28,100 --> 00:01:30,700
