I guess I was.

46
00:02:43,400 --> 00:02:45,800
Her fiancé must be
real broken up.

47
00:02:46,500 --> 00:02:47,800
Bet he misses her.

48
00:02:49,600 --> 00:02:51,300
Ted Huffard, deputy sheriff

49
00:02:51,300 --> 00:02:52,800
