Brenda MacDowell was abducted.

56
00:03:05,100 --> 00:03:06,800
August 12, '07.

57
00:03:07,600 --> 00:03:09,700
Car's a late-model
gold Honda Accord.

58
00:03:09,700 --> 00:03:11,100
Driver's side dent.

59
00:03:11,500 --> 00:03:12,900
Reported stolen
in Grays Ferry

60
