144
00:07:20,600 --> 00:07:22,300
Blood, DNA.

145
00:07:22,400 --> 00:07:24,000
Already got enough
to put you away.

146
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:25,600
Don't need you saying jack.

147
00:07:26,900 --> 00:07:28,700
Then why are we taking
the scenic route,

148
00:07:28,700 --> 00:07:30,800
