to find her body?

149
00:07:32,700 --> 00:07:36,500
Give you a chance to
help yourself, cooperate.

150
00:07:36,800 --> 00:07:38,800
We'll talk to the DA,
see what we can do.

151
00:07:39,100 --> 00:07:40,200
You a Kenso?

152
