from Kensington.

153
00:07:42,500 --> 00:07:44,000
Port Richmond maybe.

154
00:07:44,200 --> 00:07:45,700
I'll ask the questions.

155
00:07:45,700 --> 00:07:47,000
Kensington.

156
00:07:50,200 --> 00:07:53,300
