for food this way, bathroom.

157
00:07:53,300 --> 00:07:55,100
Guess you'll have
to hold it.

158
00:07:57,700 --> 00:07:59,200
Your perfume.

159
00:07:59,500 --> 00:08:00,900
It's flowery.

160
00:08:01,500 --> 00:08:04,200
