from someone in your position.

161
00:08:04,700 --> 00:08:05,800
Don't wear it.

162
00:08:06,700 --> 00:08:08,100
Cologne then.

163
00:08:08,800 --> 00:08:10,200
It's aftershave.

164
00:08:11,800 --> 00:08:13,500
