going to turn off her lights.

234
00:11:16,900 --> 00:11:18,700
RUSH:
She saw the world
a certain way.

235
00:11:19,000 --> 00:11:20,400
The way she wanted it to work.

236
00:11:20,400 --> 00:11:21,500
SMITH:
Makes a person

237
00:11:21,500 --> 00:11:23,100
